 to state with most having a leaving age of 16 or 17, but a handful having a leaving age of above that number. Students who complete a certain level of secondary education (high school '') may take a standardized test and be graduated from compulsory education, the General Equivalency Degree. Gifted and talented students are also generally permitted by several states to accelerate their education so as to obtain a diploma prior to attaining the leaving age. Young people may seek employment at 14 in many states but, in practice, most employers seek someone slightly older. However, it is common for those aged 14 (and even younger) to gain employment in agriculture. * Varies by State or Territory Answer:\n"]}]},{"cell_type":"code","source":["# CELL 7: Run Baseline 1 on a small dev slice and inspect predictions   (Same as Dhru)\n","\n","def normalize_text(s):\n","    return \" \".join(str(s).lower().strip().split())\n","\n","def exact_match(pred, gold):\n","    return normalize_text(pred) == normalize_text(gold)\n","\n","def run_baseline1_example(example, max_input_len=4096, max_new_tokens=32):\n","    question = example[\"question\"]\n","    gold = example[\"answer\"]\n","    context = build_all_paragraphs_context(example)\n","    prompt = build_qa_prompt(question, context)\n","\n","    inputs = tokenizer(\n","        prompt,\n","        return_tensors=\"pt\",\n","        truncation=True,\n","        max_length=max_input_len\n","    ).to(device)\n","\n","    input_len = inputs[\"input_ids\"].shape[1]\n","    truncated = (input_len >= max_input_len)\n","\n","    with torch.no_grad():\n","        outputs = model.generate(\n","            **inputs,\n","            max_new_tokens=max_new_tokens,\n","            num_beams=4,\n","            early_stopping=True\n","        )\n","\n","    pred = tokenizer.decode(outputs[0], skip_special_tokens=True).strip()\n","\n","    return {\n","        \"question\": question,\n","        \"gold\": gold,\n","        \"pred\": pred,\n","  